bareos-fd-proxmox-plugin (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging.
  * Plugin source from bareos/bareos@0090141 with GID-fix patch.
  * Wrapper vzdump-bareos resets gid to 0 before exec to satisfy pmxcfs
    SO_PEERCRED check (bareos-fd runs as gid=124/bareos).
  * Adds mode option (default: stop) and start_new_session=True.

